--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 2.3.1 (2018-10-20)
E: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 2.3.0 (2018-07-01)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.2-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.1-RELEASE

* Version 2.2.0 (2018-05-22)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 2.1.2 (2018-04-24)
E: Simplify role by removing 'template' option

* Version 2.1.1 (2018-04-04)
E: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 2.1.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 2.0.0 (2018-02-20)
E: Simplify and improve Ansible role

* Version 1.1.1 (2017-10-18)
E: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 1.1.0 (2017-08-26)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.1-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.0-RELEASE

* Version 1.0.0 (2017-08-01)
E: Stabilize, improve and cleanup Ansible role

* Version 0.9.1 (2017-04-16)
E: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 0.9.0 (2016-10-14)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.0-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE

* Version 0.8.3 (2016-09-03)
E: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 0.8.2 (2016-05-29)
E: Improve FreeBSD support

* Version 0.8.1 (2016-05-27)
E: Improve packaging tasks

* Version 0.8.0 (2016-05-21)
F: Add support for Ansible 2.0

* Version 0.7.0 (2016-04-09)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.2-RELEASE

* Version 0.6.2 (2016-04-02)
E: Update support information for OpenBSD 5.9

* Version 0.6.1 (2016-03-08)
E: Minor Ansible role improvements

* Version 0.6.0 (2016-01-21)
F: Drop support for OS family 'Gentoo'

* Version 0.5.1 (2015-11-17)
E: Add missing Ansible tags

* Version 0.5.0 (2015-08-13)
F: Add option 'denyhosts_allowed_hosts_hostname_lookup'
F: Update 'Gentoo' configuration files

* Version 0.4.2 (2015-01-12)
B: Create inexistent directory before managing file

* Version 0.4.1 (2015-01-07)
B: Fix incorrect default variables

* Version 0.4.0 (2014-12-29)
F: Add support for OS family 'FreeBSD'
E: Various small Ansible and Jinja2 improvements

* Version 0.3.1 (2014-09-11)
E: Change license from 'GPLv2' to 'Simplified BSD License'

* Version 0.3.0 (2014-08-28)
F: Add support for OS family 'FreeBSD'

* Version 0.2.0 (2014-08-14)
F: Remove support for OS family 'RedHat'

* Version 0.1.5 (2014-08-14)
E: Improve conditional statements

* Version 0.1.4 (2014-08-07)
E: Improve default value of 'denyhosts_smtp_subject' option

* Version 0.1.3 (2014-07-20)
E: Modify default value of 'denyhosts_smtp_from'

* Version 0.1.2 (2014-07-09)
B: Fix conditional statement in template

* Version 0.1.1 (2014-05-26)
B: Move file configuration from 'install' to 'enable' task

* Version 0.1.0 (2014-04-06)
F: Initial release
